# AKO4ALL workspace .gitignore — copied as `.gitignore` during scaffold.
# This is workspace-side: it ignores bytecode caches and the bench wrapper's
# intermediate output file. The loop's outputs (`solution/`, `scripts/`,
# `trajectory/`, `ITERATIONS.md`, `HINTS.md`) are intentionally tracked.

# Python bytecode caches
__pycache__/
*.pyc

# Bench intermediate (moves to trajectory/ on success)
_bench_output.txt
